fg_segments: Your Privacy Is Our Priority esl-lounge.com has created this privacy statement in order to demonstrate our firm commitment to privacy.
The following discloses the information gathering and dissemination practices for this Web site: esl-lounge.com Information
Automatically Logged There is information about your computer hardware and software that is automatically collected.
This information can include: your IP address, browser type, domain names, screen size, access times and referring Web site addresses.

This information is used by esl-lounge.com for the operation of the service, to maintain and improve quality of the service, and to provide general statistics regarding use of the esl-lounge.com site.
How we use Cookies Cookies are very small text files that are stored on your computer when you visit some websites.
We use cookies to help identify your computer so we can tailor your user experience, track shopping basket contents and remember where you are in the order process.
You can disable any cookies already stored on your computer, but these may stop our website from functioning properly.
Advertisers We use an outside ad company to display ads on our site.

These ads may contain cookies. While we use cookies in other parts of our Web site, cookies received with banner ads are set by our ad company, and we do not have access to this information. esl-lounge is a participant in the Amazon Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com Registration Forms

Our site's registration forms sometimes require users to give us contact information (like their name, e-mail, and postal address), and demographic information (like their zip code, age, or geographical location).
Contact information from the registration forms is used to maintain and improve quality of the service, and to provide general statistics regarding use of the esl-lounge.com site.
External Links This site contains links to other sites. esl-lounge.com is not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of such Web sites.
Choice/Opt-Out Our site provides users the opportunity to opt-out of receiving the site newsletter.
You can send e-mail to the webmaster Data Quality/Access

This site gives users the following options for changing and modifying information previously provided: Contacting the Web Site If you have any questions about this privacy statement, the practices of this site, or your dealings with this Web site, you can contact us

raw_html:
Privacy Policy



Your Privacy Is Our Priority
esl-lounge.com has created this privacy statement in order to demonstrate our firm commitment to privacy. The following discloses the information gathering and dissemination practices for this Web site: esl-lounge.com 
Information Automatically Logged
There is information about your computer hardware and software that is automatically collected. This information can include: your IP address, browser type, domain names, screen size, access times and referring Web site addresses. This information is used by esl-lounge.com for the operation of the service, to maintain and improve quality of the service, and to provide general statistics regarding use of the esl-lounge.com site.
How we use Cookies
Cookies are very small text files that are stored on your computer when you visit some websites. 
We use cookies to help identify your computer so we can tailor your user experience, track shopping basket contents and remember where you are in the order process.
You can disable any cookies already stored on your computer, but these may stop our website from functioning properly.
Advertisers
We use an outside ad company to display ads on our site. These ads may contain cookies. While we use cookies in other parts of our Web site, cookies received with banner ads are set by our ad company, and we do not have access to this information. 
esl-lounge is a participant in the Amazon Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com
Registration Forms
Our site's registration forms sometimes require users to give us contact information (like their name, e-mail, and postal address), and demographic information (like their zip code, age, or geographical location).
Contact information from the registration forms is used to maintain and improve quality of the service, and to provide general statistics regarding use of the esl-lounge.com site.
External Links
This site contains links to other sites. esl-lounge.com is not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of such Web sites. 
Choice/Opt-Out
Our site provides users the opportunity to opt-out of receiving the site newsletter.
You can send e-mail to the webmaster
Data Quality/Access
This site gives users the following options for changing and modifying information previously provided: 
Contacting the Web Site
If you have any questions about this privacy statement, the practices of this site, or your dealings with this Web site, you can contact us
